DESCRIPTION: This code example demonstrates how to update the rendering method from the deprecated ReactDOM.render to the new ReactDOM.createRoot API introduced in React 18.
SOURCE: https://github.com/reactjs/react.dev/blob/main/src/content/blog/2024/04/25/react-19-upgrade-guide.md#2025-04-23_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
