TITLE: Handling Chat Room Connections
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript snippet illustrates handling real-time chat room connections. It uses `useState` for server URL management and `useEffect` to establish connections based on state changes. Dependencies include `createConnection` for managing the connection lifecycle and `showNotification` for displaying messages.
