SOURCE: https://github.com/reactjs/react.dev/blob/main/src/content/learn/extracting-state-logic-into-a-reducer.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function handleAddTask(text) {
  dispatch({
    type: 'added',
    id: nextId++,
    text: text,
  });
}

function handleChangeTask(task) {
  dispatch({
    type: 'changed',
    task: task,
  });
}

function handleDeleteTask(taskId) {
  dispatch({
    type: 'deleted',
    id: taskId,
  });
}
```

