TITLE: Implementing calculateWinner Function for Tic-Tac-Toe
DESCRIPTION: A helper function that checks if a player has won the game by examining all possible winning combinations of three squares in a row.
SOURCE: https://github.com/reactjs/react.dev/blob/main/src/content/learn/tutorial-tic-tac-toe.md#2025-04-22_snippet_33

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
function calculateWinner(squares) {
  const lines = [
    [0, 1, 2],
    [3, 4, 5],
    [6, 7, 8],
    [0, 3, 6],
    [1, 4, 7],
    [2, 5, 8],
    [0, 4, 8],
    [2, 4, 6]
  ];
  for (let i = 0; i < lines.length; i++) {
    const [a, b, c] = lines[i];
    if (squares[a] && squares[a] === squares[b] && squares[a] === squares[c]) {
      return squares[a];
    }
  }
  return null;
}
```

