TITLE: Removing Unnecessary Object Dependencies in React useEffect
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to remove unnecessary object dependencies in a useEffect hook. It creates the options object inside the effect instead of during rendering, reducing unnecessary effect re-runs.
