TITLE: Posts Tab with Artificially Slow Rendering - React JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: The PostsTab React component (memoized for optimization) simulates slow rendering by creating 500 SlowPost items, each introducing a 1 ms delay in JavaScript using a while loop and performance.now(). SlowPost displays its index as a list item. Dependencies include React memo and performance API. Main inputs are none; produces an unordered list of simulated posts. Designed to demonstrate pending state UI and transition responsiveness.
